  "detailed_description": "Please make sure your computer supports unicode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This Is A Chinese Chess Game.</h2>To win the game, you need to kill the enemy's general, that is , to achieve \"Checkmate\".<br>The current game version contain the following features:<br>Basic scene with Chessboard, pieces, and some furniture~<br>The \"Artificial Idiot\" support on single player so that you can play with computer AI.<br>Steam achievements system...<br>With Steam Workshop, you can create and upload your own AI design and scenes.<br>Multiplayer through internet (because there aren't many players, you may need a friend to start a match)<br><br>Contact via QQ<br>QQ group：678755273",
  "about_the_game": "Please make sure your computer supports unicode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This Is A Chinese Chess Game.</h2>To win the game, you need to kill the enemy's general, that is , to achieve \"Checkmate\".<br>The current game version contain the following features:<br>Basic scene with Chessboard, pieces, and some furniture~<br>The \"Artificial Idiot\" support on single player so that you can play with computer AI.<br>Steam achievements system...<br>With Steam Workshop, you can create and upload your own AI design and scenes.<br>Multiplayer through internet (because there aren't many players, you may need a friend to start a match)<br><br>Contact via QQ<br>QQ group：678755273",
